ship. Box 4, 970, care of Pool & Co., Fleet Street, E.C."—I answered that advertisement—in reply I got this letter, dated July 13th, addressed from 156, Stamford Street, and with the heading, "South & South-West Coast Steam Trawling & Fishing Syndicate" (Ex. 2, enclosing "complete doc
